OL,6,FA man has been charged with stalking
OL,7,FStrictly Come Dancing judge Shirley
OL,8,FBallas.
OL,10,FKyle Shaw, 37, appeared at South
OL,11,FSefton Magistrates' Court on 3
OL,12,FJanuary, a spokesman for the courts
OL,13,Fservice confirmed.
OL,15,FThe defendant, of Birkenhead in
OL,16,FWirral, Merseyside, is charged with
OL,17,Fstalking Ballas, 64, between 31 August
OL,18,F2017 and 29 November 2023 by sending
OL,19,Fher online messages.
